Want more details about buying Auto Likes?

What is Auto Rating?
• Automatic Likes service; 24/7 likes are sent by the system to all your posts (photo/picture, video, album) that you will share throughout the month.
• Likes are valid for post-purchase posts, not pre-purchase photos.

How does auto like work?
• When purchasing the package, you write us your username, we define your username to the system, and the system checks your account at any time and checks whether a new post is made, the system sends as many likes as you purchased to that post when a new post is made.

So, do the likes come right away, is it possible to schedule?
• Whatever you say will happen, if you say come quickly, the Like you bought will come within 10 minutes at the latest, right after the post is made.
• If you want it to come slowly and piecemeal, we can divide the likes you receive into 10, 20-minute intervals and send them slowly, like an organic like, within hours.

Who are these Likers, who will like me?
• Our users in this Package are real, foreign accounts. If you want Turkish and real likes, please contact us and ask for Turkish likes.

Do the likes drop?
• No Likes do not drop.

What does auto like do?
Thanks to auto appreciation;
• You will rank higher in tags faster,
• Since the likes come from real accounts, you can appeal to more audiences,
• It will be easier for you to exit the Discover section and your followers can find your page more easily,
• If you have many followers, you will catch the follower like rate and it will be an original impression.
• More likes will show your sales page as more original and brand.
• Your Page's posts will appear on your followers' Home Page and even in your followers' discoveries.

How will I make the payment?
• You can make the package with Prepaid cards such as Credit, Debit or ninal.
• You can make the package via Wire Transfer, Eft or ATMs of the banks where we have accounts, with or without a card.

Account security
• We definitely do not want a password.
• Within this service, your account will not be able to like pictures or follow accounts except for what you want.
It is a completely reliable and clean system.
• In general, no problem has been seen so far in uploading likes to phone-approved and mail-approved accounts.
